items.description:
这个ti+lora 的组合是我很久之前的工作了，现在看来依然好用。当然，你也可以只用我的ti，而使用别人的lora。

This ti+lora set is something I worked a long time ago, and it still works well.Of course, you could just use my ti and use someone else's lora.

Model

同时使用ti和lora你能在绝大部分模型中都得到不错的效果。

Using ti and lora together you can get good results in most models.

Why ti+lora?

ti和lora一起用能在照片基础的模型上工作的更好，而且不用写一大堆tag。

有时候你不能加太多人物lora的权重，就需要人物ti来补充人物特征。

Use both TI and Lora works very well with photrealistic models,and you don't neet to write a lot of tags.

Sometimes you can't add too much weight to the character lora, so you need character ti to complement the character characteristics.

example:

Realistic:

1girl,(weihua:1.0), <lora:Mika_Misono_Lora:0.65>, (ulzzang-6500:0.3)

normal:

1girl,(weihua:1.0), <lora:Mika_Misono_Lora:0.65>

items.name: Dual Fighting pose set
items.description:
This is a new set of poses to the collection. This set contains a total of 30 unique dual poses, Each pose has been captured from 25 different angles, giving you a wide range of options.

Please keep in mind that due to the more dynamic poses, some images may need to be resized to fit your specific needs.

All the images in the set are in png format with the background removed, making it possible to use multiple images in a single scene without worrying about overlapping backgrounds. Additionally, the Controlnet system does not require a background to use the images, so they can be imported as they are.

However, some poses may be too far from the scene and require zooming in for stable diffusion to capture them properly.

Some poses in the set, such as those with extreme angles like top-down or bottom-right upward views, may be challenging for stable diffusion to comprehend without additional prompts support. If stable diffusion is unable to understand or generate these extreme poses, it is advisable to move on to other poses.

items.name: Tera Patrick
items.description:
A request of @Dingo00.

This model currently has 2 versions:

Version 1.1 is step 1000. At first I uploaded it as an "early access" version, but, after extensive testing, I've decided it's by far the best and the most accurate one.

Version 1.0 is step 1850. You can also obtain fantastic results with it, I think, but overall I feel her facial features are not as realistic as in 1.1.

Both versions are quite NSFW, I must warn you, though. So, if you don't want Tera flashing her boobs at the earlist opportunity, you might want to add some negative prompt to that effect. :)

You probably know I haven't done many TIs based on pornstars (actually, only one if I'm not mistaken), but Tera Patrick is a special beauty, so she's an exception. This is not an attempt to capture her late 90s looks, though, since there are not many quality pics of that era online (at least that I could find). The pictures I've used for her dataset are more of the mid 2000s to early 2010s era.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

IMPORTANT NOTICE:

Hello everyone! Lately in the comments I have often seen people complaining that my LoRA are similar to each other or are not representative of the style they should represent. My models are not trained on material from other artists, and it is therefore difficult to explain what the actual output should be. Since preparing the material necessary for the publication of a LoRA usually takes me a day's work, I have therefore decided not to post all my LoRAs on CivitAI anymore, but from today I will only post those that I consider interesting enough for the audience of this site. If you are interested in downloading the other LoRA as well, you will find them all for FREE (and they'll always be) on my Patreon page (subscribers will have early access to each of these). Thank you all for your support!

I've started a community on Deviant Art to share images made with my models/LoRAs! Join here if you are interested!

IF YOU ARE NEW TO STABLE DIFFUSION OR YOU HAVE PROBLEMS WITH MY MODELS, GO HERE: Guide

IF YOUR PICTURES HAVE PROBLEMS, CHECK MY FAQ SECTION: FAQs

What's new in V2?

V2 is improved in every way possible. It has been trained on a larger, fine-tuned dataset, with more diverse poses and colors. Can easily do SFW and NSFW and has a way more consistent style.

What's this LoRA

This is a LoRA trained on a particular style. It creates illustrations with a vintage Disney cartoon style. It is also available as a checkpoint here: https://civitai.com/models/33707/mistoonamethyst

The images in the examples (v2) are created using only this LoRA and my Mistoon_Sapphire model:

You don't need to specify a word to trigger this LoRA.

The LoRA works also on NSFW (check last examples).

The images are created using different weights (you can check on the image generation panel)

items.name: Liloi_血族Bloodline：莉萝艾
items.description:
角色为国漫《血族：bloodline》系列女主角，莉萝艾。此漫画一直是我心中的白月光，尽管作者爱欧与漫友的版权纠纷已停更数年，但本人仍一直在等待后续。

训练这个模型是出于情怀，因为素材均为漫画内容，所以不可避免的在生成时相对较易产生水印或文字内容，推荐添加“text“”watermark”等负面提示词和正面提示词“very long hair”以控制质量。

我认为作者是一位勇敢的斗士，也是一位无谋的勇士，为了夺回版权，他甚至不得不卖原稿度日，如果你喜欢这个模型，也有闲钱，可以去爱发电为原作者提供一份力量。

This character is the female lead of the Chinese animation series 《血族：bloodline》, Liloi. This comic has always been my favorite, even though it has been on hiatus for several years due to copyright disputes between the author(爱欧) and “ComicFans”(A publishing company). However, I am still awaiting its continuation.

Training this model was driven by my emotional attachment to the series, and as the source material is all from the comic, it is inevitable that watermarks or textual elements may appear in the generated outputs. It is recommended to add negative prompt such as "text" or "watermark" and prompt such as "very long hair" to control the quality of the generated images.

漫画原作者爱发电：https://afdian.net/a/iomanga
